      <description>&lt;p&gt;Puoi trovare &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;Warner Bros Hogwarts Legacy - XBox One&lt;/a&gt; qui:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41mLHJYaNWL._SL500_._SL400_.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Warner Bros Hogwarts Legacy - XBox One&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;ℹ️:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Il tuo personaggio è uno studente, il cui talento potrebbe essere la chiave di un antico segreto che minaccia di distruggere il mondo magico.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Leredità che lascerai è solo tua da plasmare. Scrivi la tua storia&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Vivi a Hogwarts nel 1800.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cavalcatura Ippogrifo d’Ossidiana è sempre inclusa solo con preorder&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Scopri la sensazione di vivere a Hogwarts mentre forgi alleanze, combatti i maghi oscuri e infine determini il fato del mondo magico.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;🛒 Acquista qui!!&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&gt;&#xA;   Check the price of this item in other countries:&lt;p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=tolees0a-21&#34;&gt;🇬🇧 United Kingdom&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=tolees-20&#34;&gt;🇺🇸 USA&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.de/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=tolees0ca-21&#34;&gt;🇩🇪 Germany&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.es/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=tolees-21&#34;&gt;🇪🇸 Spain&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.fr/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=tolees0d-21&#34;&gt;🇫🇷 France&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;🇮🇹 Italia&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.ae/dp/B08KJR56PC/?tag=rdkn01-21&#34;&